- Xac thuc email qua token (`/api/auth/verify-email`)
- Gui lai email xac thuc (`/api/auth/resend-verification`)
- Quen mat khau (`/api/auth/forgot-password`)
- Dat lai mat khau (`/api/auth/reset-password`)
