- Lay thong tin nguoi dung hien tai (`/api/auth/me`)
- Cap nhat ho so ca nhan (`/api/auth/profile`)
- Cap nhat avatar (`/api/auth/profile/avatar`)
- Xoa mem tai khoan (set INACTIVE) (`/api/auth/account`)
- Social login redirect endpoint (Google/Facebook OAuth2)
- Forward trang reset password HTML (`/auth/reset-password`)

