## 12) MODULE MESSAGING (RABBITMQ DTO + CONSUMERS)

### 12.0 Chat realtime (WebSocket + STOMP + MongoDB)
- Tao/Lay phong chat cua customer (`GET /api/chat/rooms/me`) theo rule 1 customer = 1 room
- Gui/nhan tin nhan realtime 2 chieu Customer <-> Admin (STOMP)
- Luu lich su chat vao MongoDB qua RabbitMQ persist event pipeline
- Lay lich su tin nhan theo phong co paging (`GET /api/chat/rooms/{roomId}/messages?page=0&size=20`)
- Admin inbox: danh sach tat ca room, sap xep theo room vua nhan tin gan nhat (`GET /api/chat/admin/inbox`)
- Upload file/anh dinh kem qua HTTP (`POST /api/chat/upload`) roi gui URL qua websocket
- Read receipt (Da xem): danh dau da doc theo room (`POST /api/chat/rooms/{roomId}/read` + STOMP read event)
- Unread count/cham do:
- Lay unread count qua REST (`GET /api/chat/unread-count`)
- Realtime unread qua STOMP channel cho customer/admin
- STOMP channels da san sang:
- Send: `/app/chat.send`, `/app/chat.read`
- Subscribe room: `/topic/chat.room.{roomId}`
- Subscribe read receipt: `/topic/chat.room.{roomId}.read`
- Admin inbox realtime: `/topic/chat.admin.inbox`
- Admin unread realtime: `/topic/chat.admin.unread`
- Customer unread realtime: `/user/queue/chat.unread`

### 12.1 Message contracts
- EmailMessage
- AvatarUpdateMessage
- CartSyncMessage
- PromotionUsageMessage
- InventoryCommandMessage
- OrderCancelledEvent
