## 14) CAC CHUC NANG CROSS-CUTTING

- Chuan hoa response API theo wrapper thong nhat: `message`, `status`, `statusCode`, `data`
- Global exception handler theo format thong nhat
- JWT + role-based authorization
- Redis cache cho mot so nghiep vu (search/promotion/...)
- MongoDB cho chat history
- RabbitMQ event-driven cho cac luong bat dong bo
- WebSocket + STOMP cho realtime chat
- Scheduler auto-cancel VNPAY qua han
- Ho tro upload file (avatar, product thumbnail, product images)
- Tai lieu API theo tung module trong thu muc `ApisDocument`

